# Food Delivery App
Microservice based application for food delivery


### Build
To run the applciation, you need to have docker and docker-compose installed on your machine. Change the environment variables in the docker-compose.yml file for each of the services.

```yml
      - SPRING_DATASOURCE_URL=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/fd_user?useSSL=false
      - SPRING_DATASOURCE_USERNAME=root
      - SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD=root
```

and run the following command:

```yml 
docker-compose up --build
```